      "id": "PopularPost124602",
      "post_content": "Yes, true, but not many decks are built around that sort of thing. And if your deck DOES have those cards, yeah, don't use it. But that's the same sort of thing as, say, not using big fatties in a weenie deck. Or similar.   \n  \nAlso, sunburst counts the color of mana used to pay for something, it doesn't care about the basic lands you have out. This would work just as well in a sunburst deck as a mountain.  \n  \nIn the vast majority of decks, it's not worse than a mountain at all.",
      "posted_by": "Magnor_Criol",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost124602\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">Yes, true, but not many decks are built around that sort of thing.  And if your deck DOES have those cards, yeah, don't use it.  But that's the same sort of thing as, say, not using big fatties in a weenie deck.  Or similar. <br/><br/>Also, sunburst counts the color of mana used to pay for something, it doesn't care about the basic lands you have out.  This would work just as well in a sunburst deck as a mountain.<br/><br/>In the vast majority of decks, it's not worse than a mountain at all.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '124602'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy50569\">Magnor_Criol</span>\r\n                                (2/23/2011 10:14:02 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\