      "id": "PopularPost119361",
      "post_content": "Mountains are better than this card.   \n  \nThe benefit of Hammerheim's special ability pales in comparison to being able to obtain an extra mana from having [Gauntlet of Power](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gauntlet of Power) in play, or any sort of card that utilizes basic lands as a basis for determining power (i.e., cards with domain or sunburst, or [Barrel Down Sokenzan](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Barrel Down Sokenzan) , [Ben-Ben, Akki Hermit](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ben-Ben, Akki Hermit ) , [Fire Dragon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fire Dragon), [Goblin Charbelcher](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Goblin Charbelcher), [Rockslide Ambush](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rockslide Ambush), [Seismic Strike](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Seismic Strike), [Spire Barrage](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spire Barrage), [Spitting Earth](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spitting Earth)).",
      "posted_by": "AmericanVigor",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost119361\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">Mountains are better than this card.  <br/><br/>The benefit of Hammerheim's special ability pales in comparison to being able to obtain an extra mana from having <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Gauntlet of Power\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gauntlet of Power\">Gauntlet of Power</a> in play, or any sort of card that utilizes basic lands as a basis for determining power (i.e., cards with domain or sunburst, or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Barrel Down Sokenzan\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Barrel Down Sokenzan\">Barrel Down Sokenzan</a>\t, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Ben-Ben, Akki Hermit \" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ben-Ben, Akki Hermit \">Ben-Ben, Akki Hermit </a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Fire Dragon\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fire Dragon\">Fire Dragon</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Goblin Charbelcher\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Goblin Charbelcher\">Goblin Charbelcher</a>, \t<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Rockslide Ambush\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rockslide Ambush\">Rockslide Ambush</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Seismic Strike\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Seismic Strike\">Seismic Strike</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Spire Barrage\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spire Barrage\">Spire Barrage</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Spitting Earth\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spitting Earth\">Spitting Earth</a>).</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739